      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; simulation setup is performed by experienced analysts following documented SOPs.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup and execution are governed by a documented standard operating procedure reviewed by a senior engineer. Formal use-error analysis is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed."
