      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; turbulence model selection is justified by literature precedent for similar rotating blood pump geometries.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model is selected based on published precedent for FDA benchmark simulations. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2 and is deferred to higher-risk applications."
    },
    {
