      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; nominal input values are taken from published material characterisation and device specifications.",
      "rationale": "Blood analogue fluid properties and pump geometry are taken from the FDA benchmark specification. Sensitivity analysis of input uncertainty is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed."
    },
    {
