      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; sample-to-sample variability in the FDA benchmark is documented in the published dataset.",
      "rationale": "The FDA PIV dataset reports inter-run repeatability. Statistical characterisation of test-sample variability is not required at MRL 2 and has not been independently assessed."
