    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-review-board",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are explicitly scoped out as not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is judged credible for predicting worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in support of Class II CPB device pre-market submission. The assessment team notes that the intended use scope is described in the claim and requirement documentation; the structured context-of-use object was not included in this Minimal-profile package submission.",
